{"tid":2442441,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★高盛唱淡港交所，對市場仍繼續上調其盈利預測感到驚訝","createTime":"2021-03-11T10:56:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-11T10:57:40.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2b2c5569fe616f5ced42472a846179227bf4bb67","tid":2442441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"高盛對於港交所公布去年業績後，<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>市場仍繼續上調其盈利預測感到驚訝</strong></span>，相信市場忽略北水具周期性、流入速度在年內將放緩的因素。<br />\n<br />\n高盛重申對港交所給予「沽售」評級，目標價由415元下調至400元。至中午收市，港交所升3.5%，報460.4元，與目標價潛在跌幅達13%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/597924/%E5%8C%97%E6%B0%B4%E7%B8%AE%E6%89%8B-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%94%B1%E6%B7%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9F%AD%E8%A6%96-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E8%25A8%258A%2F597924%2F%25E5%258C%2597%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E7%25B8%25AE%25E6%2589%258B-%25E9%25AB%2598%25E7%259B%259B%25E5%2594%25B1%25E6%25B7%25A1%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25A4%25E6%2589%2580-%25E5%25B0%2588%25E5%25AE%25B6-%25E7%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E7%259F%25AD%25E8%25A6%2596-%25E8%25B2%25A1%25E7%25B6%2593%25E8%25A9%2595%25E8%25AB%2596&d=XsjoyflP4JPXBkuZaWCkHYdddMXd0Scb%2F0m37zAf7q8%3D&h=f1e7a72f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A/597924/%E5%8C%97%E6%B0%B4%E7%B8%AE%E6%89%8B-%E9%AB%98%E7%9B%9B%E5%94%B1%E6%B7%A1%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%A4%E6%89%80-%E5%B0%88%E5%AE%B6-%E7%9C%8B%E6%B3%95%E7%9F%AD%E8%A6%96-%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E8%A9%95%E8%AB%96</a>"},{"pid":"3a117a21a82e69314f75025ee2c2d43111882713","tid":2442441,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-11T10:57:40.000Z","msg":"高盛已犯國安法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fac